{"data":[{"name":"94:1","price":"（預言者*よ、）われら*はあなたのため、あなたの胸を広げてやった¹のではないか？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6091,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　つまり信仰、預言者*としての使命、知識、英知を受容できるよう、心を広げ、柔らかくされた、ということ（アル＝バガウィー５：２７４参照）。家畜章１２５、ター・ハー章２５も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam nashraḥ laka ṣadraka ","translations":["Have not","We expanded","for you","your breast","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","nashraḥ","laka","ṣadraka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,750],[2,750,1500],[3,1500,1960],[4,1960,3515]]}},{"name":"94:2","price":"そして、あなたから、あなたの重荷¹を下ろしてやったのだ。","arabic":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6092,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「重荷」の解釈については、「罪（勝利章２の訳注も参照）」「間違い」「預言者*としての使命につきものの苦労」といった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１０５－１０６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wawaḍaʿnā ʿanka wiz'raka ","translations":["And We removed","from you","your burden","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wawaḍaʿnā","ʿanka","wiz'raka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2970],[3,2970,4315]]}},{"name":"94:3","price":"（その重みで、）あなたの背を軋ませていたもの（重荷）を。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6093,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī anqaḍa ẓahraka ","translations":["Which","weighed upon","your back","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","anqaḍa","ẓahraka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2700],[2,2700,4140],[3,4140,5465]]}},{"name":"94:4","price":"また、あなたのため、あなたの名声を高めてやった。¹","arabic":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6094,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　預言者*としての使命を授かることなどによって、またはシャハーダ*の言葉において、彼の名がアッラー*の御名と共に言及されたり、彼への服従がアッラー*への服従と見なされたり（婦人章８０参照）、天使*たちや信仰者たちによって讃美（さんび）される（部族連合章５６とその訳注を参照）存在となることによって「名声を高められた」（アル＝バイダーウィー５：５０５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"warafaʿnā laka dhik'raka ","translations":["And We raised high","for you","your reputation","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["warafaʿnā","laka","dhik'raka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,1830],[3,1830,3465]]}},{"name":"94:5","price":"本当に、苦と共にこそ楽あり、","arabic":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6095,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-inna maʿa al-ʿus'ri yus'ran ","translations":["So indeed","with","the hardship","(is) ease","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-inna","maʿa","al-ʿus'ri","yus'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2010],[3,2010,2850],[4,2850,4445]]}},{"name":"94:6","price":"本当に、苦と共にこそ楽あり。¹","arabic":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6096,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　解釈学者らによれば、アーヤ*５と６の「苦」は同一のもので、「楽」は別のもの。つまり、一つの苦は、必ず二つの楽を伴うということ（アル＝バガウィー５：２７５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna maʿa al-ʿus'ri yus'ran ","translations":["Indeed","with","the hardship","(is) ease","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","maʿa","al-ʿus'ri","yus'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1400],[2,1400,1780],[3,1780,2650],[4,2650,4125]]}},{"name":"94:7","price":"ならば、（現世の用事から）手が空いたら、（崇拝*行為に）尽力せよ。¹","arabic":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6097,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ほかにも、前者と後者がそれぞれ「礼拝、祈願」「義務の崇拝*行為、夜の任意の礼拝」「イスラーム*の教えの伝達、自分と信仰者たちの赦しをアッラー*に乞うこと」「敵との戦い、アッラー*の崇拝*」であるといった解釈もある（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１０８－１０９参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā faraghta fa-inṣab ","translations":["So when","you have finished","then labor hard","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","faraghta","fa-inṣab",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1730],[3,1730,3565]]}},{"name":"94:8","price":"そして（あらゆる必要において）、あなたの主*にこそ希求するのだ。","arabic":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6098,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā rabbika fa-ir'ghab ","translations":["And to","your Lord","turn your attention","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","rabbika","fa-ir'ghab",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1740],[3,1740,4125]]}}],"chapter":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh","Chapter Ash-Sharh","Sharh","Surah Sharh","Chapter Sharh","Ash Sharh","Surah Ash Sharh","Chapter Ash Sharh","Surah 94","Chapter 94","The Relief","الشرح"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}